---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../../components/Tagline.astro';
import ServiceIcon from '../../components/ServiceIcon.astro';
import ServiceNav from '../../components/ServiceNav.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Integration - Wellmade" description="Intelligence that works. Not buzzwords. Practical AI that solves real problems.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary has-blobs py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <ServiceIcon name="ai" class="w-14 h-14 text-accent mb-6" />
      <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-4">Services</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">AI Integration</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        Intelligence that works. Not buzzwords.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mt-4">
        AI is everywhere. Most of it is hype. We build AI that solves real problems. Practical, reliable, integrated into products people actually use.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why It Matters -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Why it matters.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Everyone wants to "add AI" now. But bolting a chatbot onto your product isn't a strategy.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Real AI integration means understanding what intelligence can actually improve - and what it can't. It means choosing the right approach, not the trendiest one. It means building something that works reliably, not a demo that impresses for five minutes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        We've been here before the hype. We'll be here after.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Looks Like -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What it looks like.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">AI-native products.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Building new products with intelligence at the core - not added as an afterthought.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Integrating AI into existing products.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Adding capabilities to what you already have. Document processing. Smart search. Content generation. Recommendations. Automation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Choosing the right approach.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Off-the-shelf APIs, open-source models, fine-tuned solutions, or something custom. We help you pick what fits your problem, your budget, and your constraints.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Local and sovereign options.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Need to keep data on-premise? We build AI that runs where you need it, not just in someone else's cloud.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Get -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">What you get.</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-body">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>AI capabilities integrated into your product or workflow</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Clear architecture decisions, documented and explained</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Models and pipelines you understand and control</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>Performance monitoring and iteration plan</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
          </svg>
          <span>No black boxes - you know how it works and why</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who It's For -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>Product teams who want to add AI capabilities</li>
            <li>Companies exploring what AI can do for their business</li>
            <li>Organizations with data they want to unlock</li>
            <li>Anyone who tried a chatbot plugin and wants something real</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who it's not for.</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-white/80">
            <li>"We need AI" without a problem to solve</li>
            <li>Clients expecting magic without investment</li>
            <li>Projects where data privacy is an afterthought</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-white/90 mt-6 font-medium">Let's talk first. We'll be honest about what AI can and can't do for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work Together -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">How we work together.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We work in days. Flexible, transparent, no surprises.
      </p>
      <a href="/working-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-primary/70 transition-colors group">
        See how we work
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Let's add some intelligence.</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ServiceNav current="/services/ai-integration" />
  <Tagline />
</Layout>
